[metadata]
Name:Chain Lightning deals 3 to any target
Goal:Win
Turns:2
Difficulty:Easy
Description:P0 casts Chain Lightning ({R}) at Player 2. Chain Lightning "deals 3 damage to any target" (CR 601.2c). With a single Mountain the spell is castable and Player 2 goes from 20 to 17. The optional "then that player may pay {R}{R} to copy this spell" chain (DB$ CopySpellAbility | Defined$ Parent) is the documented engine gap mtg-152 and creates no copy; this puzzle asserts the PRIMARY 3-damage mode resolves and that NO misleading "copies spell" gamelog line is emitted for the unimplemented Parent-source copy.

